§7§oThis gate lets you convert vanilla redstone signals (not red alloy) into bundled colors, depending on the strength of the signal coming in.

0 = white
1 = orange
2 = magenta
3 = light blue
4 = yellow
5 = lime
6 = pink
7 = gray
8 = light gray
9 = cyan
10 = purple 
11 = blue
12 = brown
13 = green
14 = red
15 = black
